snippet.title: Three Kingdoms: Hero Wars Pre-registration Opened
snippet.description:
Beautiful Visuals, hundreds of legendary heroes, explore an epic world.
Pre-register now to get [Limited SSR], [Exclusive Avatar Frame] and [Ten Draws]!

More information: 
◆ GooglePlay: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=threekingdoms.herowars.zbgame.gp
◆ AppStore: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1616456718
◆ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ThreeKingdomsHeroWars
◆ Twitter: https://twitter.com/tkHeroWars
